title: Peta E‑Dagang Malaysia
monthlyVisitsContent: Lawatan purata laman web bulanan antara April 2017-Jun 2017
appInstallSources: Jumlah minimum muat turun applikasi menurut Google Play
contentEmployees: Sumber: LinkedIn. Data akan dipaparkan sebagai (n/a) jika bilangan pekerja tidak dipaparkan
contentMerchants:
E-dagang yang menerima lebih daripada 100,000 pengunjung setiap bulan atau 100,000 pengikut media sosial layak untuk senarai ini.
Industri-industri berikut tidak termasuk dalam senarai ini: e-tiket, perkhidmatan kewangan, perkhidmatan sewa, insurans, perkhidmatan penghantaran, makanan & minuman, meta-carian, kupon dan laman web cashback. Semua yang disebut dalam senarai ini diasaskan oleh individu dan dimulakan dalam sektor e-dagang.

contentMerchants:
E-commerce who received more than 100,000 visitors per-month or 100,000 social media followers are qualified for this list.
The following industries were not included in this list: e-ticketing, financial services, rental services, insurance, delivery service, food & beverage, meta-search, couponing and cashback websites. All mentioned in this list was founded by individuals and was initiated in the e-commerce sector.
